rows.label: tlk47100041_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm practically the only
urban Phonex you'll find
here in Invidia, though...

rows.label: tlk47100041_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I hear we're all over the
place. Even on Avaritia, where
there's not a tree in sight!

rows.label: tlk47100041_02_msg0003
rows.name:
And here I thought that the
Phonexes on the outside were
all country bumpkins...

rows.label: tlk47100041_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I suppose the kids on Avaritia
think the same of me.

rows.label: tlk47100041_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Well that's a bit irritating.
I'll have to pay a visit
to Avaritia one day!
